title: DC 52 (COMIC PACK) [ZINC] (incomplete)
description:
If you downloaded my previous torrents that were released in 3 parts just put all the files contained in each folder (NewDC 52 part 1, NewDC 52 part 2, NewDC 52 part 3) in one folder and name it NewDC 52

Download this torrent and point your torrent client to that folder and it should check the files and continue the download.
I had to upgrade my utorrent to be able to make the torrent file smaller for thepiratebay to accept it as 2.2.1 version i was using only allowed up to 4MB pieces and it gave me a torrent bigger than 200kb witch is the limit here.
Newest utorrent allows 16Mb....
Sorry for any inconvenience.

This is ZINC description on his original torrent and it explains why this is an incomplete pack.

"This pack is response to a request of the DC 52 comics packs more so the early ones but in reality to do that would take a lot of work and effort so instead i have compiled together the DC 52 packs into one super torrent.

THE DC 52 PACK is by no means complete so if you WANT a complete up to date pack then keep on walking. I hope to finish of this pack when i have more time, at 27 gig its one of the largest packs i worked on myself to try and compile.

Once again due to having no free time and not wanting to keep this on hold i thrown it out to the you guys maybe someone will finish it off or add to it :-)"
